snippet.title: Sherlock Holmes Nemesis
snippet.description: Sherlock Holmes adventures showcase two of the greatest figures in detective literature who will square off in a 3D adventure unlike any other. You can download Sherlock Holmes Nemesis aka Sherlock Holmes vs Arsene Lupin at http://www.frogwares.com/
